'''I Evropa''' ('''Europa''') si yek mashkar le 7 Barodvipenge la [[Phuv]]yake, kay, andi kadaya situatsiya si buteder yek sanskrtipnaski tay forovipnaski rikyaripen sar yek phuvipnaski. Jeolojikanes, Evropa si yek Subbarodvip vay yek bari pashdvip, o mai okchidentutno kotor la [[Evrasiya]]ko.

O baripen la Evropyako si 10&nbsp;390&nbsp;000 km<sup>2</sup> thai o gin le manushenge si 705,000,000, vai opretele 11% katar le manushenge la sundalake.

